o: Joe Samuel Ironside (born 16 October 1993) is an English professional footballer who plays as a striker for EFL League One club Cambridge United. Ironside started his career at Sheffield United after progressing through their academy. He spent time on loan at FC Halifax Town, Harrogate Town, Alfreton Town and Hartlepool United before signing for Alfreton in 2015.
